main event: Seven witnesses in New York reported seeing an off-white star-like object with lights moving in various directions on the night of March 25, 1966.
interesting points: The object was described as having both a red light and a blue-white light on top while spinning fast,The sighting lasted for about 7 minutes,There were other credible witnesses who corroborated the sighting,The object climbed rapidly before disappearing,The incident was reported to Project Blue Book for further investigation.
witness description: credible individuals who reported similar sightings
